00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:03.020
 And of course when the child is old enough 

00:00:03.020 --> 00:00:06.260
 to be put into the great social world, 

00:00:06.400 --> 00:00:08.740
 then all restrictions related to the playing ground become 

00:00:08.740 --> 00:00:11.305
 placed immediately on the child. 

00:00:11.305 --> 00:00:13.785
 And that is a very unforgivable landscape, because 

00:00:13.785 --> 00:00:15.515
 the last thing a child wants, really, the last 

00:00:15.515 --> 00:00:18.785
 what a child wants is not to have friends. 

00:00:18.975 --> 00:00:21.815
 Or even, maybe, just as seriously, 

00:00:21.820 --> 00:00:23.840
 don't have a best friend. 

