 Ah, I recently read something so idiotic that I couldn't believe it, so 

00:00:27.240 --> 00:00:29.180
 the newest prince, 

00:00:29.575 --> 00:00:32.655
 so Queen Elisabeth's great-grandchild, 

00:00:32.655 --> 00:00:35.255
 is in childcare in England. 

00:00:35.255 --> 00:00:37.785
 And in this daycare they don't let the children have a best friend, 

00:00:37.785 --> 00:00:41.195
 because that is unfair. I thought, you know 

00:00:42.795 --> 00:00:45.155
 sometimes you see something that is so stupid 

00:00:45.155 --> 00:00:47.545
 that you can't even believe it really exists. 

00:00:47.545 --> 00:00:49.525
 And this is an example of that, 

00:00:49.525 --> 00:00:52.345
 because it has long been known that 

00:00:52.345 --> 00:00:54.855
 one of the milestones in the development 

00:00:54.940 --> 00:00:58.000
 those children undergo, somewhere between the age 

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:01.080
 5 and 10 is that they choose a best friend. 

00:01:01.300 --> 00:01:04.240
 * stuttering * 

