 But anyway there are these limitations that develop 

00:02:09.645 --> 00:02:12.855
 in the social landscape. You must have friends, 

00:02:12.855 --> 00:02:15.595
 and you also need a specific person like 

00:02:15.595 --> 00:02:18.515
 particularly unique among these friends, 

00:02:18.515 --> 00:02:21.675
 giving you a real, mutual and caring relationship. 

